The Grim Adventures of Billy and Mandy
'''The Grim Adventures of Billy and Mandy''' is an animated children's [[TV]] show about an young boy named Billy [[retard|who is very accident prone and not too bright]]. His co-star, [[loli|Mandy]], [[You have no friends|is technically his only "friend"]] and never smiles (she was seen smiling out of her own accord in the first episode, however) because she is [[hardcore|''gothik as all hell.'']] Grim is the Grim Reaper, who uses his scythe and otherworldly powers to entertain and amuse them. [[Shit nobody cares about|He was forced to be their best friends to the death in the first episode when Billy and Mandy beat him in a game of Limbo IN Limbo]].

